Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.12,00:00:25.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,There's more of them than before.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.16,00:00:30.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The river's waters flow without end,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.37,00:00:34.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,yet the water is never the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.54,00:00:42.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,In still pools, foam floats, dissolving and coming forth,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.08,00:00:45.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,never remaining for long,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.08,00:00:53.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,just as man and his dwellings in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.08,00:00:58.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, Mii-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.12,00:01:02.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.25,00:01:07.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yuki-senpai, you got kept late again?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.83,00:01:10.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm terrible at classical Japanese.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.08,00:01:14.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I kind of like it. Want me to help?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.08,00:01:16.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.04,00:01:19.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I can't believe you understand this hard stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.08,00:01:21.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's the "Hojoki."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.20,00:01:24.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,My friend liked it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.45,00:01:26.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Isn't this amazing, Mii-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.08,00:01:28.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What's amazing?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.91,00:01:32.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,This is a letter from someone long ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.50,00:01:36.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,From about 800 years ago, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.54,00:01:39.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's more of an essay than a letter, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.33,00:01:42.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,800 years!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.08,00:01:46.41,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Someone from that long ago \Ncan tell us their feelings today!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.41,00:01:48.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Aren't letters amazing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.66,00:01:55.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I can see that you really get excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.58,00:01:56.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Okay then,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.95,00:01:59.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,shall we begin?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.08,00:02:04.04,Caption,,0,0,0,,School Living Club
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.70,00:02:07.37,Caption,,0,0,0,,Cause you wanna do it, if you wanna do it
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.37,00:02:09.25,Caption,,0,0,0,,When you wanna do it, you wanna do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.25,00:02:10.58,Caption,,0,0,0,,Let's do it together! (Yeah!)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.70,00:02:13.58,Caption,,0,0,0,,We are right here
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.75,00:02:16.95,Caption,,0,0,0,,We have dreams here, too
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.12,00:02:20.08,Caption,,0,0,0,,If you're talking about buddies,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.12,00:02:20.08,Caption2,,0,0,0,,you're talking about your friends! (That's right!)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.08,00:02:23.25,Caption,,0,0,0,,I tried saying "I love you!" (I love you so much!)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.83,00:02:40.08,Caption,,0,0,0,,You know what you have to do after school
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.08,00:02:41.41,Caption,,0,0,0,,Come on, now, get together!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.41,00:02:43.25,Caption,,0,0,0,,Don't sneak off to go home! (Hey!)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.25,00:02:46.41,Caption,,0,0,0,,How about club? Let's get something done!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.54,00:02:48.95,Caption,,0,0,0,,Don't go playing around!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.95,00:02:52.83,Caption,,0,0,0,,That girl says "I'm back" (Welcome back!)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.83,00:02:56.00,Caption,,0,0,0,,We'll be fine as long as we're together (Club!)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.00,00:02:59.25,Caption,,0,0,0,,Everybody say: let's all be friends
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.25,00:03:00.79,Caption,,0,0,0,,Cause you wanna do it, if you wanna do it
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.79,00:03:02.70,Caption,,0,0,0,,when you wanna do it, you wanna do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.70,00:03:04.04,Caption,,0,0,0,,I love you so much! (Yeah!)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.04,00:03:07.16,Caption,,0,0,0,,We are enjoying our lives
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.16,00:03:10.20,Caption,,0,0,0,,We're having fun 24 hours a day
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.66,00:03:13.66,Caption,,0,0,0,,The red sun shines bright on the roof
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.66,00:03:17.08,Caption,,0,0,0,,I tried shouting out to it (We're doing great!)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.08,00:03:20.08,Caption,,0,0,0,,We are right here
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.08,00:03:23.37,Caption,,0,0,0,,We have dreams here, too
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.66,00:03:26.75,Caption,,0,0,0,,If you're talking about buddies,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.66,00:03:26.75,Caption2,,0,0,0,,you're talking about your friends! (That's right!)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.75,00:03:29.87,Caption,,0,0,0,,I tried saying "I love you!" (I love you so much!)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.45,00:03:35.95,Caption,,0,0,0,,Letters
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.29,00:03:37.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Brrr!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.79,00:03:41.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The wind's really awful at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.08,00:03:42.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.41,00:03:46.41,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,We're fine now, but we've got to think of \Nhow to deal with the cold before winter comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.87,00:03:48.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Winter, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.41,00:03:50.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Doesn't even feel like it's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.04,00:03:52.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Did Yuki go to bed already?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.87,00:03:55.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yes, she was studying until late,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.54,00:03:57.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,so she's out like a light.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.12,00:04:00.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.20,00:04:06.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We should go to sleep soon, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.37,00:04:09.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hey, Prez.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.33,00:04:12.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Have you ever imagined that this was a dream,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.29,00:04:18.45,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,and you were just gonna wake up \Nand be at school as usual?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.87,00:04:22.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I dream of it every night.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.08,00:04:41.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yuki-chan,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.66,00:04:44.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yuri-san and I have decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.37,00:04:46.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Ri-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.33,00:04:50.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yes, we're going to do something fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.75,00:04:52.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,How can this be fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.83,00:04:59.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We're going to start a club, all together.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.33,00:05:04.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,A... club?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.08,00:05:06.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.91,00:05:11.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We're all going to start the School Living Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.70,00:05:17.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yuki-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.00,00:05:20.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Senpai, it's time to wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.70,00:05:24.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Morning, Mii-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.87,00:05:27.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I had a nightmare.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.50,00:05:29.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What happened in it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.12,00:05:32.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.54,00:05:34.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.25,00:05:37.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Breakfast is ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.50,00:05:39.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The others are already there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.37,00:05:40.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I see, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.75,00:05:42.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Huh? Where's Megu-nee?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.37,00:05:44.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.75,00:05:48.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, Megu-nee, good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.87,00:06:03.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,This should be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.33,00:06:11.33,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,The School Living Club is gonna \Ndo its best today, Megu-nee.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.75,00:06:16.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It looks so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.25,00:06:19.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Let's eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.37,00:06:23.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Wow, this is so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.29,00:06:25.41,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,They are green onions grown by \Nthe Gardening Club, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.41,00:06:27.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm glad they shared them with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.41,00:06:28.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.16,00:06:38.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,This udon is really great, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.79,00:06:39.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.16,00:06:43.04,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,As always, she's scarfing it down, \Nnot listening to a word you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.04,00:06:46.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hey, slow down, you're not a dog like Taromaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.87,00:06:50.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, I think Taromaru has better manners than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.16,00:06:54.58,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,It's amazing how you've managed to \Nkeep the room temperature up lately!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.58,00:06:56.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The udon's so springy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.66,00:06:58.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The miracle of modern technology, I say.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.95,00:07:02.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'd say so, yes. It lets us have warm udon as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.29,00:07:05.70,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,It's all thanks to the solar panels \Nand storage batteries here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.70,00:07:08.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Most schools don't have those kinds of things, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.20,00:07:10.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That was great!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.08,00:07:12.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Ri-san, seconds, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.12,00:07:16.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Yuki-chan, we don't have any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.87,00:07:20.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We went for variety over quantity on the field trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.25,00:07:22.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.37,00:07:25.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But wasn't the field trip fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.87,00:07:28.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We got to make friends with Mii-kun, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.37,00:07:30.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Th-thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.95,00:07:32.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It was quite the ordeal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.95,00:07:35.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yes, a terrible ordeal...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.75,00:07:40.66,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,And on the way back, we had to cram \Nall four of us and Taromaru into that little car.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.20,00:07:44.45,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,I fell asleep right away, \Nso I don't remember much of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.45,00:07:48.87,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,That's right, I was driving, \Nand Ri-san was in the passenger seat,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.87,00:07:51.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,and Taromaru was jumping all over the back seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.54,00:07:55.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm surprised you guys managed to sleep through that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.54,00:07:56.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.95,00:07:58.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,There were only two in the back?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.33,00:08:01.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.41,00:08:04.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That car...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.79,00:08:08.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,had space for four, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.00,00:08:10.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.04,00:08:15.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Me, and Ri-san and Kurumi-chan,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.29,00:08:18.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Mii-kun and Megu-nee.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.95,00:08:20.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And that's four?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.20,00:08:22.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.58,00:08:32.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.37,00:08:34.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Where was Megu-nee?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.54,00:08:42.25,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,O-oh, back then, remember, you were \Nsleeping so you probably didn't know,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.25,00:08:47.70,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,but Megu-nee said her house was really close, \Nso she got out and walked back, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.70,00:08:49.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.58,00:08:51.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,She did?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.12,00:08:52.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.95,00:08:53.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.33,00:08:58.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.70,00:09:00.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yuki-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.33,00:09:03.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna go ask Megu-nee!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.16,00:09:05.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.25,00:09:08.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.00,00:09:09.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's nobody's fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.08,00:09:13.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yuki-senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.45,00:09:17.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's not good for her to go on like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.25,00:09:19.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Miki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.45,00:09:24.25,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,I know that Senpai's smile \Nreally makes everyone feel better.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.95,00:09:26.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But that doesn't mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.33,00:09:28.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.25,00:09:33.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm sure Megu-nee feels the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.29,00:09:37.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Megu-nee?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.95,00:09:40.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You're really here, right, Megu-nee?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.20,00:09:43.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.20,00:09:48.83,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Even if I don't have much of a presence, \NI won't leave you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.00,00:09:52.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But sometimes I get really scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.83,00:09:56.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Sometimes I can't remember things, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.87,00:10:01.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Everyone has fuzzy memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.37,00:10:07.37,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,That's why you have to talk to \Nother people or keep a diary.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.08,00:10:12.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Then those memories won't be so fuzzy anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.95,00:10:16.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's what I believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.95,00:10:20.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Even if the person you remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.45,00:10:27.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,...isn't here anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.08,00:10:37.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'll work hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.66,00:10:41.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'll work really hard, Megu-nee.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.75,00:11:04.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.29,00:11:06.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hey, you're back!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.79,00:11:08.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.91,00:11:12.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Mii-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.79,00:11:14.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I told you not to touch me so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.79,00:11:18.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Mii-kun, I just kinda missed you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.16,00:11:19.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I don't care, jeez!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.83,00:11:22.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Mii-kun, Mii-kun, something smells weird!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.54,00:11:23.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.75,00:11:26.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I don't mean you, I mean Taromaru, Taromaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.54,00:11:30.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hey there, boy, what's going on with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.08,00:11:32.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Taromaru doesn't want to get in the bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.20,00:11:34.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.45,00:11:37.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'll put him in the bath, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.62,00:11:43.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.08,00:11:49.70,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Now that I think of it, the world as we see it \Nmust look so different to dogs.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.04,00:11:51.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.45,00:11:56.87,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,I hear that dogs can't see colors like we do, \Nso they see the world in sepia tones.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.37,00:12:00.58,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,But because of that, \Nthey have really good night vision,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.25,00:12:04.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,and can even see some ultraviolet light.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.29,00:12:08.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And dogs can smell things that we can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.29,00:12:12.83,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,All the flowers we see, \Ndogs have no idea what color they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.83,00:12:15.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Huh, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.08,00:12:18.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Gimme back my hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.45,00:12:25.75,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Don't you get the feeling the two of them \Nsee the same world?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.70,00:12:28.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.00,00:12:29.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.08,00:12:36.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Even the four of us see the world in different ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.41,00:12:41.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hey, Taromaru! Jeez!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.70,00:12:43.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.33,00:12:46.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yuki-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.50,00:12:47.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.83,00:12:49.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Ow, ow, ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.12,00:12:52.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Please don't overdo it, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.33,00:12:54.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm fine, I'm fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.58,00:12:55.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.29,00:12:57.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.00,00:13:01.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Looks like they belong to Megu-nee.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.75,00:13:04.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What a mess...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.41,00:13:05.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'll help.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.12,00:13:08.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.16,00:13:10.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You're a club member now,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.12,00:13:13.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,so you don't have to thank me so politely.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.08,00:13:15.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.75,00:13:17.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.00,00:13:19.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hey guys, look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.87,00:13:22.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Wanna write a letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.66,00:13:27.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I think it's a good idea to write a letter,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.54,00:13:29.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,but how are we gonna send them?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.12,00:13:30.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.50,00:13:32.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The post office is outside school!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.00,00:13:34.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You hadn't even realized that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.20,00:13:39.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Then, why don't we send them from the school?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.79,00:13:43.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Writing a letter makes me think of carrier pigeons!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.20,00:13:46.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Where are we supposed to find a carrier pigeon?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.33,00:13:48.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We'll go catch one!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.54,00:13:50.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But how are we going to catch one?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.87,00:13:52.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,With this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.29,00:13:53.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You're going to beat it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.83,00:13:56.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Nah, I'm just gonna hit it with the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.12,00:13:57.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.08,00:13:57.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Whaaa...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.37,00:13:58.20,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Whaaa...? \NAnd this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.20,00:13:58.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's not going to work...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.45,00:13:59.45,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,That's not going to work... \NAnd this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.45,00:13:59.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's not going to work...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.91,00:14:00.75,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,You don't even need to hit them in the first place. \NAnd this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.75,00:14:01.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You don't even need to hit them in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.04,00:14:02.12,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,You don't even need to hit them in the first place. \NAnd this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.41,00:14:04.87,Caption,,0,0,0,,Expands to 20 times
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.41,00:14:04.87,Caption2,,0,0,0,,their size!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.41,00:14:04.87,Caption3,,0,0,0,,Balloons
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.87,00:14:04.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Why don't we use these?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.12,00:14:07.95,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Oh, aren't those the ones you \Npicked up in the test of courage?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.37,00:14:12.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,If we blow them up, they won't fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.50,00:14:13.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.95,00:14:20.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I wish we had helium.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.79,00:14:24.58,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Oh, I think the Scuba Club \Nmight've been using some.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.12,00:14:27.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You had a Scuba Club?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.00,00:14:28.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Way back when, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.45,00:14:30.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'm gonna go check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.37,00:14:31.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.91,00:14:33.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You can't carry the tank on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.95,00:14:35.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'll come help.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.37,00:14:36.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.95,00:14:37.41,Caption,,0,0,0,,Ri-san
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.16,00:14:37.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.41,00:14:39.41,Caption,,0,0,0,,Mii-kun
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.41,00:14:39.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm a club member, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.12,00:14:42.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Alright, if you could.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.62,00:14:43.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.20,00:14:45.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'll go too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.66,00:14:47.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Why don't you stay and write a letter, Yuki-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.79,00:14:49.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.58,00:14:51.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'll write one, a really good one!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.16,00:15:01.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I wonder if anyone will find our letters.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.41,00:15:04.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I think someone will.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.62,00:15:09.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's not like all of mankind has disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.37,00:15:11.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Y-yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.95,00:15:14.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's a really small chance, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.00,00:15:17.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I hope they do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.58,00:15:20.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.33,00:15:24.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hmmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.29,00:15:26.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.66,00:15:29.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's kinda embarrassing to write really formally.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.75,00:15:32.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And my handwriting sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.62,00:15:35.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.25,00:15:37.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Let me borrow this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.25,00:15:39.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What're you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.08,00:15:43.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're making a paper doll?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.45,00:15:44.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.83,00:15:50.29,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Yuki-chan, how would you feel \Nif you were walking along
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.29,00:15:53.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,and found a letter attached to a balloon?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.66,00:15:54.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.25,00:15:57.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'd be really surprised! And happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.45,00:16:00.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Would you think about their handwriting?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.95,00:16:02.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Nope!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.54,00:16:05.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'd just be happy to get a letter!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.45,00:16:06.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.00,00:16:10.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.08,00:16:14.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We're back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.12,00:16:18.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We're back. We found a helium tank!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.20,00:16:25.33,Caption,,0,0,0,,Helium
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.62,00:16:21.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And we brought a trap, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.45,00:16:24.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You're still thinking about catching a pigeon?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.33,00:16:25.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hell yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.33,00:16:27.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, Mii-kun, you should write a letter, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.83,00:16:28.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Here, here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.08,00:16:30.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Alright, alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.50,00:16:32.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hey, Yuki, look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.37,00:16:33.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.91,00:16:36.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,With this trap, we can kill a pigeon in a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.91,00:16:39.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But it can't carry the letter if it's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.58,00:16:41.54,Caption,,0,0,0,,Staff #2
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.08,00:16:42.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Then I'll go catch one!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.54,00:16:44.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Have fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.45,00:16:46.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Let's move the tank towards the wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.62,00:16:47.08,Caption,,0,0,0,,Staff #2
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.62,00:16:48.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.58,00:16:48.54,Caption,,0,0,0,,Sakura
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.83,00:16:50.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Mii-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.83,00:16:52.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Y-yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.29,00:16:54.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What're you gonna write?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.29,00:16:56.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hmmm,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.04,00:16:59.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I dunno...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.87,00:17:14.33,Caption,,0,0,0,,KYAA!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.45,00:17:16.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.91,00:17:20.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I wonder what I should write in my letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.70,00:17:23.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Anything would be fine, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.00,00:17:27.12,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,You could write about yourself, \Nor what you want to do in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.87,00:17:29.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Anything you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.20,00:17:31.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,My future, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.95,00:17:34.25,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,I gotta figure out if I'm gonna \Ngo to college or get a job,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.25,00:17:36.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,or Megu-nee's gonna get mad at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.66,00:17:39.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I think everyone would get mad if you didn't figure it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.50,00:17:40.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yeah, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.12,00:17:47.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We have to leave this school eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.75,00:17:48.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.91,00:17:50.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Graduation, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.20,00:17:52.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.83,00:17:56.37,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Why don't we write about our dreams \Nfor after graduation!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.37,00:17:58.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Our dreams for the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.41,00:18:00.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yeah, and then we can write,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.66,00:18:05.29,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,"We're doing well and working hard \Nto achieve our dreams!"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.08,00:18:12.79,Caption,,0,0,0,,MY DREAM
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.08,00:18:12.79,Caption2,,0,0,0,,I want to do so many things.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.08,00:18:12.79,Caption3,,0,0,0,,There's not enough space in this letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.08,00:18:12.79,Caption4,,0,0,0,,I want to graduate school and...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.45,00:18:40.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Having trouble sleeping?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.41,00:18:44.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,There's a lot of them by the front door.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.37,00:18:50.25,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Looks like they don't like getting wet, \Neven now that they're like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.16,00:18:55.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I found this earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.83,00:18:58.79,Caption,,0,0,0,,Sakura
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.58,00:18:58.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It says "Sakura" on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.70,00:19:01.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Megu-nee...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.54,00:19:06.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Is it alright if I hold on to this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.75,00:19:09.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It might be helpful in some way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.75,00:19:11.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Sure, here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.00,00:19:14.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.00,00:19:19.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm sure that one day, we'll be able to leave here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.91,00:19:20.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.50,00:19:25.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I wonder when the rain will stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.70,00:19:29.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm sure it'll all be alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.45,00:19:36.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.87,00:19:38.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.79,00:19:40.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Good luck, little Pidgey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.95,00:19:43.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Wait, who the hell is Pidgey?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.29,00:19:46.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,This little guy, Pidgey Hatonishiki!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.37,00:19:48.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,No, his name is Arnold!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.04,00:19:51.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Aww, I wanna name him, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.70,00:19:53.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm the one who caught him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.12,00:19:54.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,"Pidgey" is cuter!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.95,00:19:56.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,He looks way more like an "Arnold" though!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.08,00:19:57.20,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,C'mon, you two, please stop. \NHe looks way more like an "Arnold" though!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.20,00:19:57.95,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,C'mon, you two, please stop. \NBut he looks like a "Pidgey"!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.95,00:19:59.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But he looks like a "Pidgey"!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.16,00:20:00.62,Subtitle3,,0,0,0,,Why don't you use both and name him \NArnold Hatonishiki the Second? \NIt's Arnold!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.62,00:20:03.16,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Why don't you use both and name him \NArnold Hatonishiki the Second?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.00,00:20:06.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.29,00:20:10.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Okay, his name is Arnold Hatonishiki the Second!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.37,00:20:12.37,Caption,,0,0,0,,Name:
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.37,00:20:12.37,Caption2,,0,0,0,,Arnold Hatonishiki
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.37,00:20:12.37,Caption3,,0,0,0,,the Second
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.29,00:20:12.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Where did "the second" come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.00,00:20:15.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Okay, Arnold Hatonishiki the Second.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.37,00:20:16.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Fly well!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.58,00:20:19.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,On the count of three, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.37,00:20:20.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.75,00:20:21.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,One!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.58,00:20:23.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.70,00:20:26.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.66,00:21:17.16,Caption,,0,0,0,,To Kei.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.25,00:21:17.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Kei, how are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.04,00:21:22.70,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,I'm living somewhere new and \Nmade some new friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.70,00:21:25.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm doing well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.20,00:21:28.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Taromaru is doing well, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.79,00:21:31.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's all thanks to everyone here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.79,00:21:34.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Are you fine with just being alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.20,00:21:39.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.70,00:21:42.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Living is such a wonderful thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.12,00:21:49.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The dew may fall and the flower remain,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.45,00:21:54.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,or the flower wilt and the dew remain.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.70,00:21:55.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What's that about?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.70,00:22:00.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Words my friend liked.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.41,00:22:03.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.41,00:22:06.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I hope someone finds them.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.45,00:22:20.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I hope one day our paths cross again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.50,00:22:35.95,Caption,,0,0,0,,We're doing fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.08,00:22:45.41,Caption,,0,0,0,,Bathed in the crimson light
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.41,00:22:52.08,Caption,,0,0,0,,What were you thinking of?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.62,00:22:58.54,Caption,,0,0,0,,I thought you were beautiful as you tried to brush it off
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.54,00:23:03.41,Caption,,0,0,0,,Tears welling in your eyelashes
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.70,00:23:06.62,Caption,,0,0,0,,I always thought
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.62,00:23:14.29,Caption,,0,0,0,,That these days would go on forever
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.04,00:23:20.41,Caption,,0,0,0,,Without a doubt
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.33,00:23:24.41,Caption,,0,0,0,,The sky we looked up at
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.41,00:23:27.50,Caption,,0,0,0,,Looks upon us from so far away
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.50,00:23:32.75,Caption,,0,0,0,,We just gripped each other’s lost hands
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.08,00:23:36.12,Caption,,0,0,0,,Quietly, without ever changing
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.12,00:23:39.29,Caption,,0,0,0,,I’m not lonely anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.29,00:23:44.54,Caption,,0,0,0,,I just keep moving towards the other side of the ending world
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.12,00:23:52.45,Caption,,0,0,0,,I can see our sunrise
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.45,00:23:55.29,Caption,,0,0,0,,I can see it
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.29,00:24:02.00,Caption,,0,0,0,,So smile
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.04,00:24:06.95,Caption,,0,0,0,,Next Time!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.58,00:24:09.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I wonder where Arnold is now?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.79,00:24:12.00,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,He's a second generation Japanese man, \Nso maybe he went to America?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.00,00:24:13.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Wow, Arnold!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.50,00:24:15.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,He is Arnold Hatonishiki's son.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.75,00:24:17.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,How do you know all this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.62,00:24:21.00,Caption,,0,0,0,,Future
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.62,00:24:21.00,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Next time on School-Live, episode 8: \N"Future"
